                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Secundino <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>exti</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audi</ex></expan> Alpini @(obito) <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LX <lb n="4"/>Ursa <expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iux</ex></expan> <surplus>Ursa con(iux)</surplus> <lb n="5"/>viva fecit et Secun<lb break="no" n="6"/>dina filia
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Z. 1: zwischen D und M schlangenförmiger Worttrenner; am Ende hedera. Z. 2 (Ende): Palmzweig. Z. 3 (Anfang): statt S auch P möglich.</p>
